<div class="container">
<div class="container getstarted">
<br />

<h1 class="font-fam getstarth">Installing the App</h1>	
<p class="font-fam getstartp">Welcome! To have a better experience using Hallit, go to your home and add Hallit to your homescreen </p>

<h1 class="font-fam getstarth">Navigate the App</h1>
<p class="font-fam getstartp">Use the browsers back and forward icon to go back and forth during a session <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-menu-left"></span> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-menu-right"></span></p>

<h1 class="font-fam getstarth">Basic Icons</h1>	
<p class="font-fam getstartp">Get to help by tapping <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span></p>	
<p class="font-fam getstartp">Get to search by tapping <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-eye-open"></span></p>	
<p class="font-fam getstartp">Logout by tapping <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-off"></span></p>	
<p class="font-fam getstartp">Get to your home by tapping <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-home"></span> or Hallit logo </p>
<p class="font-fam getstartp">Get to your profile by tapping <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></span></p>	
<p class="font-fam getstartp">Create and upload hall by tapping <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-cloud-upload"></span></p>
<p class="font-fam getstartp">Explore more halls by tapping <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-globe"></span></p>
<p class="font-fam getstartp">View your friends activities by tapping <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-stats"></span></p>
<p class="font-fam getstartp">Get to previous by tapping <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-menu-left"></span></p>

<h1 class="font-fam getstarth">Others</h1>	
<p class="font-fam getstartp">Tap on usernames in profile to view information such as; Edit Profile and much more...</p>
<p class="font-fam getstartp">Click on photos to view them. Tap <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-heart"></span> to like  </p>
<p class="font-fam getstartp">When you find friends or channels you love, tap on the subscribe button to subscribe or unsubscribe button to unsubscribe  </p>



